Preconditions:
The input parameter `n` must be a positive integer.
The input parameter `queries` must be a non-null 2D array.

Postconditions:
The returned matrix `mat` must have the same number of rows and columns as the input parameter `n`.
The values in the returned matrix `mat` must be updated according to the queries performed.
The returned matrix `mat` must be a 2D array of integers.